8
00:00:22,509 --> 00:00:24,990
The situation is getting more complicated.

9
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:29,949
Deputy Magistrate Tan, since you work for Senior Jing,

10
00:00:29,949 --> 00:00:33,240
you should know why I came to the Southwest this time.

11
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:37,530
